# Keep LF line endings everywhere, including on Windows checkouts. Scripts and
# hooks are executed by node/bash; CRLF corrupts shebangs and shell parsing and
# silently breaks the statusline and hooks on Windows.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
*.mjs text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
